                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一言以蔽之，何伟亚的努力就是要解构马嘎尔尼使团在“现代性”话语下天然的优越地位，以及重构在“现代性”话语下清廷被掩盖的政制与文化。拆解的努力非常成功，但重构方面则还有不足。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="30209136">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-30209136" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-30209136" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="30209136">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2116608/">辄馨</a>
                    <span>2008-01-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本似乎是五年前看的吧！评价不少，口碑不好！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="643860250">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-643860250" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-643860250" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="643860250">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/47929578/">安提戈涅</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-09-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">还是萨义德的那套陈旧方法论，不过，论述礼仪和英国中产阶级俱乐部的部分有意思。史料梳理的很细致，写论文小帮手。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="77711190">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-77711190" class="vote-count">0</span>
